MEET @alexaferrmusic:
Alexa Ferr is a 28 year old bonafied multi threat artist. Alexa is a singer, songwriter, producer and dancer born and raised in Toronto, Canada living in Los Angeles, CA. With over 10 years in the industry, Alexa Ferr has collaborated with many established producers, writers and artists to build her catalog along with develop her artistry and love for music! She has released original music over the years and is gearing up for a full release of her brand new EP, with the lead single titled, “Me, Myself & I” that is currently available on all streaming platforms!
Dedicated to giving back, Alexa supports charities that deal with topics such as Children, Cancer and Domestic Violence. She hopes to use her voice to raise awareness on these issues, all which are personal to her.
